fields.name: Clear Whey Isolate
fields.description: Winner of ‘The Best Sports Nutrition Product’ in the European Specialist Sports Nutrition Awards 2019.

fields.name: Impact Whey Isolate
fields.description: Packed with 23g of protein per serving, this superior-quality blend is ideal to provide your muscles with the protein they need for growth and maintenance,1 so that you can keep making progress with your fitness goals.

fields.name: Impact Diet Whey
fields.description: A delicious shake that delivers 39g of protein per serving, along with other ingredients specifically chosen to support your weight-loss programme.

fields.name: Weight Gainer Blend
fields.description: If you’re looking to gain weight, build strength, or increase size then you’re going to have to consume more calories than you burn throughout the day — known as a calorie surplus.

fields.name: Extreme Gainer Blend
fields.description: Our Extreme Gainer Blend has been created specifically to support your bulk-up ambitions, with a huge 35g of protein per serving — perfect for building and maintaining muscle.

fields.name: Protein Meal Replacement Blend
fields.description: Being mindful about your calorie intake doesn’t mean you should give up on nutrients and taste. Our delicious Protein Meal Replacement Blend will support your weight loss goals, while providing your body with the essentials it needs.

fields.name: Vegan Protein Blend
fields.description: Vegan Protein Powder is our newly reformulated plant-based protein. We’ve improved the taste and texture, but don’t worry — it’s still packed with the amazing nutritionals you loved before.

fields.name: Soy Protein Isolate
fields.description: Soy Protein Isolate is a great choice for vegetarians, vegans, and anyone wanting to reduce the amount of dairy products in their diet. It delivers an impressive 27g of protein per serving,* with a 90% protein content* — ideal when on a plant-based diet.

fields.name: Clear Vegan Protein
fields.description: Clear Vegan Protein is our game-changing vegan protein shake. We’ve harnessed the power of high-quality pea protein isolate, infused with real fruit and added B vitamins, to create a light, tasty, fruity alternative to traditional protein shakes.

fields.name: Collagen Protein
fields.description: This blend is made with highly purified collagen peptides to give you a delicious shake with a 90% protein content*, helping you to boost your daily intake without taking on unnecessary fats and carbs.

fields.name: Slow-Release Casein
fields.description: Slow-Release Casein is our highly popular milk protein powder, designed to be slow absorbing to provide a sustained supply of protein between meals and even while you sleep.

fields.name: Clear Protein Starter Pack
fields.description: It’s never been easier to smash your goals and take your nutrition to the next level with our Clear Protein Starter Pack.

fields.name: Coffee Boost Whey
fields.description: Our Coffee Boost Whey is exactly what it sounds like — a delicious blend of high-quality whey protein with real coffee and guarana — that’s the perfect alternative to your morning coffee.

fields.name: Overnight Recovery Blend
fields.description: Our unique night-time formula combines a slow-release blend of milk protein, micellar casein, whey concentrate, and egg white powder, to help grow and maintain muscle — all while you sleep.
